or and control effort. The optimal trajectory may\nthen be achieved by a low-level tracking controller. We demonstrate our\napproach with an example of a reference satellite in Sun-synchronous orbit\npassing over globally-distributed, Earth-observation targets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Feb 2021 03:34:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
